Company Overview of China Railway Signal & Communication Corporation Limited



Snapshot People




Company Overview
China Railway Signal & Communication Corporation Limited, together with its subsidiaries, provides rail transportation control system solutions in the People's Republic of China and internationally. The company operates through Rail Transportation Control System, Construction Contracting, and Others segments. It offers engineering design, consultancy, and system integration services for rail transportation control system projects, and integrated solutions designed to achieve functionality and performance of control system. It also manufactures and sells signal system products; communication information system products; cables, and electrical appliances and equipment; and signal automatic, el...
China Railway Signal & Communication Corporation Limited, together with its subsidiaries, provides rail transportation control system solutions in the People's Republic of China and internationally. The company operates through Rail Transportation Control System, Construction Contracting, and Others segments. It offers engineering design, consultancy, and system integration services for rail transportation control system projects, and integrated solutions designed to achieve functionality and performance of control system. It also manufactures and sells signal system products; communication information system products; cables, and electrical appliances and equipment; and signal automatic, electronic, and electrical equipment for railways and urban transit, as well as electric power basic equipment and devices. In addition, the company provides construction, installation, testing, and maintenance services for rail transportation control system projects; urban rail transit technical development, consultation, and related service; project investment, management, and consultation services; and construction and installation contracting services, as well as technical detection services. Further, it is involved in the provision of municipal engineering and related construction services; and import and export of goods, as well as offers survey, design, and consultation services. Additionally, it engages in trading of equipment in communication, signal, electric power and automatic control, minerals, coal, coke, and other materials; and designing, manufacture, sale, and training of tramcars, light rail vehicles, and pipe fittings, as well as provides industrial and civil construction contracting services. China Railway Signal & Communication Corporation Limited was founded in 1953 and is headquartered in Beijing, China. China Railway Signal & Communication Corporation Limited operates as a subsidiary of China Railway Signal & Communication Corporation.
Detailed Description


