Business Summary




China Railway Signal and Communication Corp operates as a rail transportation control system solution provider. The Company's main businesses are to provide one-stop solution of design and integration, equipment manufacturing and system implementation services for rail transportation control systems to its customers. The Company has three main business lines: design and integration operation, which is engaged in providing engineering design and system integration services for rail transportation control system projects, and offer integrated solutions designed to achieve functionality and performance of control system; equipment manufacturing operation, which is engaged in the manufacture and sale of signal system products, communication information system products and other products, and system implementation operation, which is engaged in the construction, installation, testing and maintenance services for rail transportation control system projects.(Source: PROSPECTUS)


