Business Summary


Provides signaling systems for railwaysChina Railway Signal & Communication Corp.Ltd. manufactures signaling systems.It operates its business through the Mainland China and Other Countries geographical segment.The firm offers one-stop solution of design and integration as well as manufactures equipment and provides train transportation controls systems services.The company was founded on December 29, 2010 and is headquartered in Beijing, China.Number of employees : 17 511 persons.
 





